verbose_text: Recent determination of the molecular structure of MtrF, an MtrC homolog, at a resolution of 3.2 A has provided the unprecedented molecular structural evidence supporting the terminal reductase role for the outer-membrane c-Cyts of S. oneidensis MR-1 in Fe (III) oxide reduction.
